snippet.title: Amber Heard Is Sabotaging Johnny Depp's Role In Fantastic Beasts 3
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Is Sabotaging Johnny Depp's Role In Fantastic Beasts 3 as their heated dual way legal suits continue to rage on. This is the most recent installment in the Amber Heard, Johnny Depp debacle, the latter got his first opportunity in a hot minute to get some work in the J. K. Rowling movie Fantastic Beasts 3. Now in what can be equated to sabotage Heard isn't letting one inch of leeway to Depp.
